{"tid":1525052,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"創興呢間野真係好好食","createTime":"2019-08-31T19:22:30.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-31T19:35:06.000Z","uid":292044,"like":4,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"e591a5a7828dc74bb02f743cafbac11f5a1483d1","tid":1525052,"uid":292044,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T19:22:30.000Z","msg":"小弟第一次開po 還請多多見諒<br />\n<br />\n話說小弟就創興嘅呢間野同啲frd食飯，食食下睇電視就見到popo推到過黎，咁無gear嘅我哋梗係唔會咁快走啦，十點零就黎十一點，都冇乜客架啦，咪坐低睇下樓下乜嘢境況先走囉。<span style=\"color: red;\">但係，喺呢個時候，有啲操大陸口音嘅店員喺度討論緊電視播緊嘅野</span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: blue;\">呢啲暴徒打死曬佢就啱㗎啦，搞亂曬個香港。</span></strong></span><br />\n呢間野真係唔洗錢都唔會想再去食，都唔知佢哋啲食材有冇加過料。大家去食嗰陣真係小心至上。<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/UfbbC3C.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FUfbbC3C.jpg&h=51f24c7f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/4iHBPai.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F4iHBPai.jpg&h=eb4166de&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"1803563840fb539bdb80a74c0d1945648eb7b184","tid":1525052,"uid":292044,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T19:22:53.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"ee0e8cf34a73d8a3da9fb60b99b2e8fbb1d6fe1c","tid":1525052,"uid":292044,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T19:23:07.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"758eb67078c6dedf7f46a75e5612fa2bf630a0c0","tid":1525052,"uid":292044,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T19:23:18.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"3e710fd83eaee058b2abc94c90b12e46048b6a2e","tid":1525052,"uid":292044,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T19:23:30.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"e1666e6ac57242a82c10fef31dc33799a299f2e8","tid":1525052,"uid":292044,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T19:23:40.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"a60e93020b8a8f2b1ef043773fa0e7f7dd0db40b","tid":1525052,"uid":292044,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"cite